== Installation instructions ==

$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install

Installs by default to /usr/local. Use ./configure --prefix=PREFIX
to override.

== Dependencies for Debian GNU/Linux systems ==

* libao-dev (ao for audio playback)
* libglib2.0-dev
* libgtk2.0-dev
* libmikmod2-dev (mikmod for tracker modules)
* libmad0-dev (mp3)
* libvorbis-dev

== Dependencies for Fedora systems ==

* gtk2-devel
* libao-devel
* libmad-devel
* libmikmod-devel
* libvorbis-devel
